CLI program for learning commands and words. The program will reward you if you
answer question right and fast. Then it will not ask the same question for a
while. So it gives you spaced repetition.

Put files in a 'lists' folder. 
Format is one expression you want to learn per line
or you can have lines with following format:
expression###definition

You might want to do backup of your lists
You dont want to have other stuff in the lists folder because lots of damage.

This program is work in progress. Use on own risk.

You need python 3

